  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"These ruins of a lighthouse have brittle bones.<br>Ocean once surrounded it. You know the stories...<br>Of a great beautiful oasis where titans came to die.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grief brought you here.<br>Now you are trapped in an endless cycle, on a world that is lost to you.\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439300/extras/7026265b7848e59fdb3dd4b2fac32125.poster.avif?t=1753861699\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439300/extras/7026265b7848e59fdb3dd4b2fac32125.webm?t=1753861699\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439300/extras/7026265b7848e59fdb3dd4b2fac32125.mp4?t=1753861699\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Part horror, part interactive poem about overcoming and bittersweet surrender, A Butterfly is an arthouse game open world flight-sim meets walking-sim with interactive fiction elements.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You must explore a world that is alien to you. Transcendence comes at a heavy price. Surrounded by a never ending desert where you learn an ancient story. The abyss called your name. You followed it here. Now you are its prisoner.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"These ruins of a lighthouse have brittle bones.<br>Ocean once surrounded it. You know the stories...<br>Of a great beautiful oasis where titans came to die.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grief brought you here.<br>Now you are trapped in an endless cycle, on a world that is lost to you.\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439300/extras/7026265b7848e59fdb3dd4b2fac32125.poster.avif?t=1753861699\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439300/extras/7026265b7848e59fdb3dd4b2fac32125.webm?t=1753861699\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3439300/extras/7026265b7848e59fdb3dd4b2fac32125.mp4?t=1753861699\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Part horror, part interactive poem about overcoming and bittersweet surrender, A Butterfly is an arthouse game open world flight-sim meets walking-sim with interactive fiction elements.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You must explore a world that is alien to you. Transcendence comes at a heavy price. Surrounded by a never ending desert where you learn an ancient story. The abyss called your name. You followed it here. Now you are its prisoner.</p>",
